fulltitle: Brian Lynch: Jazz Trumpeter & Faculty Member at NYU Steinhardt School

description:
In this clip from www.artistshousemusic.org - Brian Lynch is a jazz trumpeter and a faculty member at New York University's Steinhardt School. He has toured with Eddie Palmieri, the Afro-Caribbean Jazz Octet, and the Phil Woods Quintet. 
Brian Lynch, from NYU, gives wonderful insight into the world of the professional musician.
